  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个事件驱动架构的流程图，核心是从Aggregate产生事件开始，经过Event Store、Reactor，最后到Queue Worker执行Side Effect的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Aggregate和Event Store之间是存储事件的关系，对吧？然后Reactor负责把事件转换成任务推送到Queue？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，顺序是：Aggregate把事件存到Event Store，Event Store dispatch给Reactor，Reactor push job到Queue，然后Queue Worker去process这个job，最后执行Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把主流程画出来了，六个participant都加上了，从Store Event到Execute Side Effect的箭头也连好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加一个分支逻辑——Side Effect执行完要有成功和失败两种情况。成功的话Worker要把job标记为completed，失败的话要触发retry。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以用alt块来区分Success和Failure两个分支？Return Success和Return Failure都是从Side Effect回到Worker，然后Worker再操作Queue？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Success分支是Side Effect返回成功，Worker mark job as completed；Failure分支是返回失败，Worker retry job。两个分支都要完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Success",
        "Failure",
        "Completed",
        "Retry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了，alt块已经加上，Success和Failure两个分支都画好了，整个事件驱动流程从Aggregate产生事件到最终Side Effect执行和状态处理都完整了。",
